  <context>
    <background>
      `sprk_actiontypeid` was a lookup from `sprk_analysisaction` → `sprk_analysisactiontype` that carried
      dispatch decisions in the pre-R7 model. After R7 dispatch moves to `node.sprk_executortype`, this lookup
      has no runtime reader. Task 042 deleted the last reader (`ExecuteAnalysisAsync`'s call chain). Now the
      field can be dropped cleanly. Per FR-05, the lookup TABLE (`sprk_analysisactiontype`) is preserved as
      decorative maker categorization — DO NOT delete the table, only its FK column on `sprk_analysisaction`.
    </background>
    <dependencies>
      <dependency task="042" status="must-complete-first">Last runtime reader (ExecuteAnalysisAsync) deleted — no production code reads this field after task 042 completes.</dependency>
    </dependencies>
    <related-work>
